%% Trace: features/01-首次綁定Email建立帳號.feature + 02-首次綁定手機發送OTP + 03-首次綁定手機完成綁定.feature
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant CheckCtrl as LoginController
    participant Ctrl as BindingController
    participant Svc as FirstTimeBindingService
    participant OtpSvc as OtpService
    participant SMS as ItSmsGateway
    participant CRM as CrmCustomerGateway
    participant Repo as MemberAuthRepository
    participant OtpRepo as OtpRecordRepository

    User->>FE: 輸入聯絡方式（Email 或手機）
    FE->>CheckCtrl: POST /check-contact-identity
    CheckCtrl-->>FE: 200 {result: BIND, masked_existing_email: "u***@example.com" (CLARIFY-05)}
    FE-->>User: 顯示「我們找到您的資料，請設定密碼以綁定」

    alt Email 路徑
        User->>FE: 輸入密碼 + 密碼確認 (CLARIFY-01)
        FE->>Ctrl: POST /bind/first-time/email (email, password, password_confirm)
        Ctrl->>Svc: bindEmail(email, password, password_confirm)
        Svc->>Svc: assertPasswordsMatch(password, password_confirm)
        Svc->>CRM: lookupCustomer(emailHash)
        CRM-->>Svc: customer_id + member_id (BIND verified)
        Svc->>Repo: insert MemberAuth(customer_id, email, password_hash)
        Svc-->>Ctrl: bound
        Ctrl-->>FE: 201 Created
    else 手機路徑
        User->>FE: 輸入手機 → 發送驗證碼
        FE->>Ctrl: POST /bind/first-time/mobile/send-otp (mobile)
        Ctrl->>OtpSvc: issue(contact=mobile, purpose=REGISTER, channel=sms)
        OtpSvc->>OtpRepo: insert OtpRecord
        OtpSvc->>SMS: enqueue OTP
        OtpSvc-->>Ctrl: otp_uuid
        Ctrl-->>FE: 200 {otp_uuid}

        User->>FE: 輸入 OTP + 密碼 + 密碼確認
        FE->>Ctrl: POST /bind/first-time/mobile (otp_uuid, otp_code, password, password_confirm)
        Ctrl->>Svc: bindMobile(otp_uuid, otp_code, password, password_confirm)
        Svc->>OtpSvc: verify(otp_uuid, otp_code)
        OtpSvc-->>Svc: ok
        Svc->>CRM: lookupCustomer(mobileHash)
        CRM-->>Svc: customer_id + member_id
        Svc->>Repo: insert MemberAuth(customer_id, mobile, password_hash)
        Svc-->>Ctrl: bound
        Ctrl-->>FE: 201 Created
    end
    FE-->>User: 綁定成功，導向登入
